rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0001
rows.name: Have you ever played Money-Bye-Bye, mo?

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Alst is going through a tough time, but it's a board
game that everyone in this wheelhouse is
hooked on, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a board game I happened to find in
Luxuria, but it's pretty intense, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It's a game where you roll dice on the board,
buy and sell real estate, increase your assets,
and bankrupt your opponents, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0005
rows.name:
What's scary about this game is that you can't
show any mercy to your opponents, so the atmosphere
gradually becomes hostile, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Some people go crazy from the brutal treatment,
and it can even lead to fistfights, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Thanks to that, this wheelhouse is full of tension, mo.
I'm worried if Goldmund will be able to operate
normally tomorrow... mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_04_msg0008
rows.name: The person who came up with this is a genius... mo.
